WLAN Connection Daemon
=========================

This daemon is responsible for controlling the WLAN connection as well as 
messaging related information through the system D-Bus.

The program must be run as root because many of the Wireless extensions
require root priviledges

GConf settings
==============


wlancond D-Bus API
================

Service:
com.nokia.wlancond

Interfaces:
com.nokia.wlancond.request
com.nokia.wlancond.signal

Object paths:
/com/nokia/wlancond/request
/com/nokia/wlancond/signal

